11 8. Legally possess seventy-two (72) ounces of topical
12 marijuana.
13 B. Possession of up to one and one-half (1.5) ounces or forty-
14 two and forty-five one-hundredths (42.45) grams of marijuana by
15 persons who can state a medical condition at the time of the stop
