21 in contact with a person in violation of this subsection and who is
22 satisfied as to the identity of the person, as well as any other
23 pertinent information the law enforcement officer deems necessary,
24 shall issue to the person a written citation containing a notice to
Req. No. 10537 Page 12

1 answ er the charge against the person in the appropriate court. Upon
2 receiving the written promise of the alleged violator to answer as
